est/7.0.0/src/test/java/org_springframework/spring_test/TestClassScannerTest.java`\n\nKey changes:\n- Removed `@ClassTemplate` / `@ExtendWith(SpringExtension.class)` from the public `TestClassScannerTest`.\n- Added a nested disabled fixture class:\n  - `@Disabled(\"Fixture discovered by TestClassScannerTest\")`\n  - `@ClassTemplate`\n  - `@ExtendWith({SpringExtension.class, ...})`\n- The scanner test still scans and asserts discovery of that fixture and its nested `@Nested` classes, so it should still reach `TestClassScanner.collectNestedTestClasses()` and `Class#getDeclaredClasses()` without executing `SpringExtension` lifecycle callbacks under the older JUnit runtime.", "textSignature": "{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_0c47ffce2f44ea62016a29f2b764208190ac0184af421b0bb0\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}], "api": "openai-responses", "provider": "OCA", "model": "oca/gpt-5.5", "usage": {"input": 460, "output": 716, "cacheRead": 47616, "cacheWrite": 0, "totalTokens": 48792, "cost": {"input": 0, "output": 0, "cacheRead": 0, "cacheWrite": 0, "total": 0}}, "stopReason": "stop", "timestamp": 1781133989132, "responseId": "resp_0c47ffce2f44ea62016a29f2a630cc81909460aaa90656fd61"}, "toolResults": []}
